                     <interp inst="t17880625-28-off130" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing four silver spoons, value 30 s. and one marrow spoon, value 8 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17880625-28-victim286" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Appleton
               <interp inst="t17880625-28-victim286" type="surname" value="Appleton"></interp>
